data.title: Rev Fr Adelbert Arthur Wagner (1890
data.meta_description: Father Wagner was ordained a priest on June 13, 1920 and served the following assignments in the Diocese of Saint Cloud:  Associate Pastor of Saint Boniface Church, Melrose: 1920-1922 Pastor of Saint Theresia Church, Donnelly: 1922-1925 Pastor of Saint Charles Church, Herman: 1922-1925 Pastor of Saint Mary Church,...
